		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Rod - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>While holding the rod, you have &amp;reference[Advantage] on &amp;reference[Perception] checks and &amp;reference[Initiative] rolls.</p></li><li><p>You can cast <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.KzJ4ChPXHr2MnGbz]{Detect Evil and Good}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.zWjDq2YlL1XWOcji]{Detect Magic}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.1gqMmxF2RFCK9khd]{Detect Poison and Disease}</em>, and <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Wp9ckwdiUpIuPE5l]{See Invisibility}</em> from the rod.</p></li><li><p><strong>Action: </strong>You can plant the rod to shed Bright Light in a 60-foot radius (Dim Light for another 60 feet). While in that Bright Light, you and your allies gain a +1 bonus to &amp;reference[Armor Class] and saving throws and can sense &amp;reference[Invisible apply=false] creatures in the same light. The light lasts 10 minutes or until the rod is removed; once used, this property can't be used again until the next dawn.</p></li></ul><section class=\"secret\" id=\"foundry-secret-1\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Plant Rod</strong> activity can be used to place a 60 foot template representing the Bright Light radius. It includes an Active Effect which can be applied to the relevant Actors and adds the +1 bonus to AC and Saving Throws.</p></section>",
